Day 26: Adapt to Feedback!
🔄 "Feedback is the lifeblood of improvement—embrace it!"  
👉 Tip: Seek feedback from the team and stakeholders regularly. Adapt your approach based on what you learn.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
